Yatsurugi-jinja (八劔神社) is a [[Shinto shrine]] famous for its underwater [[Shinko-shiki]]. It has floating [[mikoshi]] that are carried by people across the water in a parade.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://morethanrelo.com/en/floating-mikoshi-miya-festival/|access-date=2023-04-12|website=morethanrelo.com}}</ref> [[:File:Miyamatsuri.JPG|[[File:Miyamatsuri.JPG|link=|220x220px]]]]
